level_lore = "Long ago, the carabao walked beside farmers as a patient companion, helping the land provide for every family. Reforged into a towering engine of endless harvests, Pasan knows only to press onward, forgetting that even the richest soil must one day rest. Beneath its steel frame lies the fading memory of a prosperity once shared with the earth."
